{"tid":1717261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG遺害已浮面］[文宣新方向]逼藍絲發起一場真正大三罷","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:30:49.000Z","uid":6097,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"490a0ecedafeb4c750dbe8fdf38423416a978408","tid":1717261,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"首先，請大家睇睇依個post<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1716862\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1716862</a><br />\n立場哥哥長出了氯痤瘡，目前唯一可確認人體積存高濃度二噁英的表徵<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n中共一早講過放棄整代人 <br />\n要地唔要人<br />\n<br />\n上面製化武+班狗瘋狂射 基本係一場<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慢性大屠殺</span></span><br />\n中環旺角我相信濃度已經非常高 <br />\n政府仲荒死毒唔死大家<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 用漂白水令佢完全揮發</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣要向依個方向去嚇死藍絲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「香港淪為大型毒氣室」<br />\n「林鄭手持市民健康作政治籌碼」</span><br />\n<br />\n藍絲係好撚自私又怕死嘅生物<br />\n不停耳濡目染 令班藍都信TG好毒 唔理自己都理個孫呀<br />\n我相信發起罷工會易好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例如三罷目的變為要求政府停止化武攻擊</span><br />\n<br />\n我相信只要由我哋化武文宣不停去累積民怨<br />\n一定可以發起真正大三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以推一推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔好再畀前線日日吸化武啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a6cc19b8f38a694987e00956805af70dc20dd3","tid":1717261,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5ebbcf3902be1d142af52cd1d182245d0b228e3","tid":1717261,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我知好長，但我希望大家睇一睇<br />\n依下資料係我開始出黑血同停m搵嘅</span><br />\n<br />\n所以政府由得班狗亂射唔係無原因<br />\n<br />\n依家tg嗰種化學物係脂溶性 水沖唔走 漂白水更加唔可用<br />\n會變為微結晶喺食物同衣物積存<br />\n<br />\n例如前線件外套長期曝露喺充滿tg嘅空氣中<br />\n佢一返屋企 <span style=\"color: violet;\">其實已經帶哂化學物畀家人同寵物</span><br />\n<br />\n你用洗衣機 啲化合物就會殘留喺洗衣機<br />\n著返件外套就=帶微結晶周街走 <br />\n<br />\n依家唔止前線手足 連普通市民都有依啲情況<br />\n我哋依家每一日都接觸緊毒氣 分別只係多與少<br />\n<br />\n香港一早有專家話無解 <span style=\"color: red;\">外國人係著生化衣洗街<br />\n要用到哥士的 <br />\n至於你啲衫褲鞋襪掉咗佢吧啦</span><br />\n<br />\n所以中共唔會怕狗權過大嘅問題 因為都心知佢哋唔會長命<br />\n依家個情況係佢哋樂於見到<br />\n食得最正係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線/中共眼中叛逆者<br />\n記者/第四權<br />\n學生/知識份仔<br />\n班狗/軍權</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正正就係中共最怕嘅四種人</span>"},{"pid":"af67982a3a94426ef44b67bfe7752f1b4007133f","tid":1717261,"uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZYHcUP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZYHcUP.jpg&h=d8756805&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18f7001802d69448e3bedb21dab87d0378db57ca","tid":1717261,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cb4a4d08fdf57fff94786b5c8963289c358990","tid":1717261,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOSXm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOSXm.png&h=e6e3ba1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f0c244f32ce224ccd3e2df1c9478baa2ad2d2b1","tid":1717261,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"你哋唔可以就咁水洗衫咖<br />\n<br />\n係沖唔走咖<img src=\"/as